OL,3,CWorkers walk out at ready meals
OL,4,Cfactory and warn supermarket shelves
OL,5,Cwill suffer
OL,7,FReady meal supplies at UK supermarkets
OL,8,Fcould be affected as workers at a
OL,9,FWrexham factory have walked out in a
OL,10,Frow over pay and working conditions.
OL,12,FUnion bosses say the Oscar Mayer
OL,13,Fworkers will be #2,000 a year worse
OL,14,Foff. They claim the walkout will hit
OL,15,Fsupermarket shelves across the
OL,16,Fcountry, including Sainsbury's, Tesco,
OL,17,FAldi and Asda.
OL,19,FMore than 550 workers voted for strike
OL,20,Faction, with a 76% turnout.
