OL,5,Cwill suffer
OL,7,FOscar Mayer says the company is
OL,8,Fdisappointed by the strike action and
OL,9,Fpublic claims they say have been
OL,10,Ffactually inaccurate.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the manufacturer
OL,13,Fsaid the changes are needed because of
OL,14,Fthe loss of a "significant customer
OL,15,Fcontract." They also say they've
OL,16,Fengaged with unions and that the
OL,17,Fcompany does not expect impact on
OL,18,Fcustomers.
OL,20,FThe Wrexham plant has 1,500 workers
OL,21,Fproducing 2 million ready meals a week.
