OL,7,F"The proposals have not been made
OL,8,Flightly but we have made clear
OL,9,Fthroughout that they are absolutely
OL,10,Fnecessary to ensure a long-term
OL,11,Fsustainable business and protect the
OL,12,Fjobs we provide in the local
OL,13,Fcommunity. These measures will also
OL,14,Fput us in line with the majority of
OL,15,Fother businesses in our sector and
OL,16,Fsimilar companies in the local area.
OL,17,FNonetheless, we have continued to
OL,18,Fengage with our colleagues to seek
OL,19,Fagreement on these proposals."
