OL,3,CWorkers walk out at ready meals
OL,4,Cfactory and warn supermarket shelves
OL,5,Cwill suffer
OL,7,FMP for Wrexham Andrew Ranger has says
OL,8,Fhe is urging the company to fully
OL,9,Fengage with workers and Unite "to
OL,10,Freach a mutually satisfactory
OL,11,Fresolution to the current situation."
OL,13,F"Employees everywhere should be
OL,14,Ftreated with respect and in good
OL,15,Ffaith. This does not appear to have
OL,16,Fhappened so far in this case. Everyone
OL,17,Funderstands that businesses sometimes
OL,18,Fmust make changes when circumstances
OL,19,Fchange," he said, adding that the
OL,20,Fchanges must be carried out in a "fair
OL,21,Fand ethical way."
