OL,7,F"Businesses such as Oscar Mayer are
OL,8,Fessential to Wrexham, the local
OL,9,Feconomy and for employment in the area
OL,10,F` I want to see them, and their
OL,11,Fworkforce succeed in partnership.
OL,13,F"Industrial action is always a last
OL,14,Fresort for workers and the decision to
OL,15,Ftake it will not have been made
OL,16,Flightly. If the company had entered
OL,17,Finto proper dialogue sooner, it could
OL,18,Fhave been avoided ` alongside the
OL,19,Fconsequential detrimental impact on
OL,20,Fboth workers and the business.
